Class AbstractDao

  • java.lang.Object
    • daos.common.AbstractDao
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ApiTokenDao, BatchDao, ComponentDao, ComponentResultDao, GroupResultDao, LoginAttemptDao, StudyDao, StudyLinkDao, StudyResultDao, UserDao, WorkerDao

    @Singleton
public abstract class AbstractDao
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract DAO: Of the JPA calls only refresh() is public - persist(), merge() and remove() are protected. The latter ones usually involve changes in different entities and should be handled by the DAO of that type.
